node.text:
@DarrenCurtis_Christies sold this AUD $8,600,000 beachfront residence located on the Central Coast of New South Wales, Australia - Pearl Beach. 

Gazing over pristine sands and crystal clear waters, 'Pearl Beach Villa' is a sophisticated contemporary home with a distinctly beachy feel. Surrounded by manicured gardens and alfresco spaces designed to take in the magical view, it provides a welcome retreat from city life.

Walls of glass, soaring ceilings and a seamless interaction between the indoors and out are the hallmarks of this stylish, light-filled residence. Unobstructed views of the Pacific Ocean, Lion Island and right across the Pittwater to Palm Beach create a breathtaking backdrop.

Along with an abundance of entertaining space, the residence's generous, highly functional two-storey floor plan encompasses four upper-level bedrooms, but easily sleeps twelve with the fourth bedroom accommodating six full-sized bunk beds. Three of the four bedrooms enjoy unrestricted views from their balconies and the main features a luxurious ensuite with a bath.

Contact @DarrenCurtis_Christies for more information
_
